_sText:
De_crackmansion_fixed is a Bomb/Defusal map created based upon the original cs_crackhouse. Bomb site A are the computer files in the office. They must be destroyed. Bomb site B is the file cabinets across the house. These also must be abolished. Both bomb sites are located on the second floor of the "crackmansion." Remember to do your objective or suffer the consequences!!!
Enjoy!
